title: Trendsylvania 3/18: Joe Biden, Snyder Cut, Olivia Munn, Armie Hammer, The Bachelor

description:
On this edition of Trendsylvania Jack and Super Producer Anna discuss conspiracy theorists thinking Joe Biden deepfaked a recent appearance, the ‘Justice League” Zack Snyder cut, Olivia Munn warns ATL shooting is symptomatic of Anti-Asian sentiment, Dom Zeglaitis; Armie Hammer accused of rape, and some 'The Bachelor' talk.
